subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Down eight points in the first half, the Huskies responded with a 12-point run in the second and rolled to a 77-53 victory over California in an N.C.A.A. tournament regional semifinal.
